('sports', 'Cricket', 'Which country won the first ever Cricket World Cup in 1975?', 'text', NULL, 'West Indies', 'They defeated Australia in the final.'),
('sports', 'Ice Hockey', 'What happens when a player is sent off for 2 minutes?', 'text', NULL, 'Minor Penalty', 'The most common type of penalty.'),
